---
title: Red Rice Bowl with Mushrooms, Spinach, and Cabbage
description: There’s no ordinary rice to be found in this recipe. Instead, our chefs used nutty-flavored red rice to bulk up the stir-fry. Not only is it jam-packed with fiber and iron, but it also lends a magazine-worthy finish to this vibrantly colored bowl.
